'''Michael Gough''' (born [[December 3]], [[1950s|1956]]) is a voice actor who has appeared in several ''[[Star Wars]]'' games.

==''Star Wars'' roles==
{{Mediacat|soundcat=Audio files of Michael Gough}}
*''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]'' &ndash; Airspeeder Pilot, [[B1-Series battle droid|Battle Droid]], [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] Hovercraft Captain, [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] Knight, [[Udopal speeder|Udopal Fast Bike]] Driver, [[Zaloriis/Legends|Zalor]] Minister [[Transe Decar]]
*''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight II: Jedi Outcast]]'' &ndash; [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] 2, [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtrooper]] Officer 2
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'' &ndash; Additional voices
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]'' &ndash; Additional voices

